    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Little Droid 2: Escape&quot; is the second part of the game. New enemies, bosses, traps, secret places are waiting for you. In the game you can improve weapons. As in the first part, the droid will have to be constantly charged to complete the entire game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When a mysterious droid tricked you into landing on an unknown planet — there was no way back.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a small exploration unit, cut off from your base and stranded in a world of ruins, traps, and forgotten technology.<br>But beneath the decay, something greater is hidden.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Somewhere in orbit lies a secret space factory — and on it, the elusive Engineer. His ship is your only chance to escape this planet. But reaching it means surviving deadly machines, abandoned facilities, and the remnants of a plan you were never meant to be part of.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore, endure, and find your way back to the stars.<br>Even if no one asked you to be here.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120410/extras/f7e664f52c9d3a9d0e523ab4735e8e40.poster.avif?t=1770650406\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120410/extras/f7e664f52c9d3a9d0e523ab4735e8e40.webm?t=1770650406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3120410/extras/f7e664f52c9d3a9d0e523ab4735e8e40.mp4?t=1770650406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
